{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And people who came on first, who tried to get a corner for themselves or their friends or family, they were squeezed into smaller and smaller and smaller spaces, and they were protesting.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you know, I just wrote about this, the three days in the wagon, so I don't want to spend too much time on it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it's fairly vivid in my mind because I was thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People tried to open their suitcases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eventually, the door got slung shut, and I could hear the lock snap.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were kids crying and mothers hushing their children, and some people moaning as if they were in pain.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was just wondering what's-- what's-- what's coming off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people were trying to open their cases, but there was no room-- enough room to open the case.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a general chaos of voices and shouts and talk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then there was a shudder, and everybody fell against each other as the train started moving.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I eventually got very hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then there was nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the next day, the train stopped and we thought we were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were wondering what's happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we could hear the wagon doors open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was coming closer to our wagon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they shouted, 'toilet stop.' And not everyone-- some people got out, and we went to the other side of the embankment to relieve ourselves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as I wrote in my little memories-- memoirs-- there was only the rain-starved grass and God and us, and the guards pointing guns at us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were, whether it was Poland or Austria or Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we got back into the car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at that time, you know, the general tenor of the sound level was quite low.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The occasional whimper of a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we got to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we got out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as we got out--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody-- you know, the second day, hunger really bad, but the third day was overriding everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I-- you know, I often-- and I must have fallen asleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I didn't tell you that after-- after a while, I wanted still to escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a pocket knife, and I tried to make a hole where I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could feel with my hand the little square that I could let myself go through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My hand got sore and bleeding, so I used the other hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this happened before the toilet rest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the toilet rest, I looked out and I saw that the locomotive was pushing the train, not pulling it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew that that was not an avenue that I could utilize.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got in the train, and-- and-- and-- and the train kept moving.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people resigned themselves to what's next.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was the third day, around midday, that we got to a place we didn't know where it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got out of the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were young men in blue and-- blue-striped clothes-- looked like pajamas-- telling us to move it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were, this time, German soldiers and dogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were told to leave everything in the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It'll be taken to our quarters where we are going to be working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no-- German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German-- German, not Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But people who understood German, they told everybody else what was being said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of Hungarian Jews spoke German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- I heard expressions like [POLISH], which I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It means fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Move it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember scrambling out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember stretching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To the left of me was beautiful, lush, green grass on the other side of the fence, with gleaming, white-painted goal posts-- a soccer field.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then in front of us was this gate that said [GERMAN], which means 'Work will set you free.' And on the right side of me was barracks and more wires.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And behind me-- I didn't know it then-- were the baths, the gas chambers, and the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as the line kept drifting along, there was this German soldier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I could see him from a distance-- polished, black boots, immaculately dressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Quite absorbed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "White gloves.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was telling people where to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, you know, my passion to look people in the eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I looked straight at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I pulled myself up to my full height.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I could see him look at me for an instant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he pointed, and I went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And about 60 of us, all men, were given-- we were shaved and shorn and sprayed and showered.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
